ote><br />\n<br />\n側訓, 有時會心口壓住番隻手</blockquote><br />\n唔好痺架咩？"},{"pid":"2a7f39524f5f38998e281edb5ee4a6a9d1750099","tid":138853,"uid":60605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點樣先可以壓住心口瞓？我今晚就想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n側訓, 有時會心口壓住番隻手</blockquote><br />\n唔好痺架咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會, 我唔識形容"},{"pid":"0e1dea31bd6559126c45f0ff8617f82aff3ef8dc","tid":138853,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>發親夢都係一個你熟悉的地方，但夢入面都係會唔同左樣<br />\n<br />\n我夢入面的地鐵站係好金屬、頹廢風<br />\n<br />\n地鐵線排位好似新宿車站咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係, 夢入面既熟悉地方會同現實有啲唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個既話，如果你相信，果度有可能係平衡時空<br />\n<br />\n我發夢都去過另一個香港，係廢墟咁的，當然都有正常版本"},{"pid":"f5ade8d57491a7c6e451524a9aad03fb627ed756","tid":138853,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"公開試果個，你可以諗下自己係咪有d 野就黎要面對，但自己又未有心理準備同實際準備好迎接挑戰？"},{"pid":"418a6d81f80dc979cb8e9c863fd1c9f779a07363","tid":138853,"uid":44896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"尋晚發夢甩牙 係咁流血 好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6549c7cb969f241a45f6b16e21bcccf313f71c76","tid":138853,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:55:43.000Z","msg":"早幾日發咗個怪夢<br />\n我同細佬喺間好大嘅屋入面賽跑 有d跑online mario kart feel咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住喺窗口見到出面有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁同細佬即刻熄晒d燈 匿埋喺床後面<br />\n點知班人一入嚟 就揾到入嚟<br />\n我同佢地講 有咩想攞即管攞 幫埋你攞都得 放過我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住同佢地落咗去廚房 打開櫃桶 同細佬打個眼色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一人拎把餐刀 鋸班賊仔頸 點知唔夠利 得唔夠深<br />\n我即刻彈開 攞咗一把菜刀 一把肉刀<br />\nd賊仔 拎咗d短嘅刀出嚟<br />\n打咗幾個回合 佢地攞埋手裡劍出嚟掉我 原來係忍者嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打多陣我投降 點知佢地話用手同我打<br />\n跟住就醒咗<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打識解夢 可以話我聽個夢其實有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d54302f24a511b1bd0614b155dd97793c5d7cf","tid":138853,"uid":60605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公開試果個，你可以諗下自己係咪有d 野就黎要面對，但自己又未有心理準備同實際準備好迎接挑戰？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢種夢，我可能耐唔耐會發一次，可能二三年度一次，但我出嚟做左野十年"},{"pid":"d52e8857fc857fcff041741c6b82e30c0c581d63","tid":138853,"uid":60605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾日發咗個怪夢<br />\n我同細佬喺間好大嘅屋入面賽跑 有d跑online mario kart feel咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住喺窗口見到出面有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁同細佬即刻熄晒d燈 匿埋喺床後面<br />\n點知班人一入嚟 就揾到入嚟<br />\n我同佢地講 有咩想攞即管攞 幫埋你攞都得 放過我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住同佢地落咗去廚房 打開櫃桶 同細佬打個眼色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一人拎把餐刀 鋸班賊仔頸 點知唔夠利 得唔夠深<br />\n我即刻彈開 攞咗一把菜刀 一把肉刀<br />\nd賊仔 拎咗d短嘅刀出嚟<br />\n打咗幾個回合 佢地攞埋手裡劍出嚟掉我 原來係忍者嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打多陣我投降 點知佢地話用手同我打<br />\n跟住就醒咗<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打識解夢 可以話我聽個夢其實有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n近排出switch 所以聯想到mario kart game<br />\n大屋似係睇完西片果啲好撚大間既古堡<br />\n鋸頸似係之前ISIS 段片喎<br />\n呢啲零零memory 喺夢境裏組埋做一個故事"},{"pid":"6bc6bfa395dcf87de3ac78a62b7b0665c6b18fa2","tid":138853,"uid":60605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T10:00:49.000Z","msg":"有無人試過發夢打波，自己會跳得好高，好易入樽？"},{"pid":"71ae097226154536da7a0b3922253ab7c6da6905","tid":138853,"uid":60605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c66072703d0aa10ef66d9cc29c6f5eb2f25f26f","tid":138853,"uid":7223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"呢排成日發喪屍夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30b720894518d650514e4c4be5234b59b7863d0","tid":138853,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早幾日發咗個怪夢<br />\n我同細佬喺間好大嘅屋入面賽跑 有d跑online mario kart feel咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住喺窗口見到出面有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁同細佬即刻熄晒d燈 匿埋喺床後面<br />\n點知班人一入嚟 就揾到入嚟<br />\n我同佢地講 有咩想攞即管攞 幫埋你攞都得 放過我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住同佢地落咗去廚房 打開櫃桶 同細佬打個眼色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一人拎把餐刀 鋸班賊仔頸 點知唔夠利 得唔夠深<br />\n我即刻彈開 攞咗一把菜刀 一把肉刀<br />\nd賊仔 拎咗d短嘅刀出嚟<br />\n打咗幾個回合 佢地攞埋手裡劍出嚟掉我 原來係忍者嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打多陣我投降 點知佢地話用手同我打<br />\n跟住就醒咗<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打識解夢 可以話我聽個夢其實有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n近排出switch 所以聯想到mario kart game<br />\n大屋似係睇完西片果啲好撚大間既古堡<br />\n鋸頸似係之前ISIS 段片喎<br />\n呢啲零零memory 喺夢境裏組埋做一個故事</blockquote><br />\n但係我連isis d片都冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb60083f20247e244314d557e0244cc3896560de","tid":138853,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:06:00.000Z","ms